title: Sibling Watchery - Drag Race All Stars Season 7 - Episode 10
itunes:author: Sibling Rivalry & Studio71
content:encoded:
Bob and Monét review Episode 10 of All Stars Season 7 in their best British accents as the queens take the stage to roast each other at the first-ever Kennedy Davenport Center "Hall of Shade" Honors. Pulitzer prize-winning journalist, Ronan Farrow, joins the esteemed judges' panel.
